items.title: LIVE: Kamala Harris to preside over 2024 election certification, four years after Capitol riot
items.author: Reuters
items.content:
U.S. Vice President Kamala Harris says she will certify the 2024 election as the Electoral College vote count is underway at a joint session of Congress. This comes four years after a mob of Trump supporters stormed the Capitol in a failed bid to overturn his 2020 loss. She will announce the results and declare Donald Trump as the winner of the presidential election ‚Äî a formality Trump asked his then-Vice President Mike Pence not to do four years ago.
